\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marcus slept dreamlessly, or at least it seemed so to him. He knew from college psych classes that}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf4  [everyone would dream multiple dreams every night,] }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 but he definitely didn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t remember dreaming this time. Which seemed weird given everything that happened. The moment he opened his eyes on the pitch black chamber he\u8217\'92d been in since the System arrived, the lights in the chamber gradually brightened and he was confronted with a System message.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 <$Scr_Ps::0>Introduction time remaining: 86:51:18}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Initiating Second Evaluation in 03:41:18<!$Scr_Ps::0>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Some quick mental math told him he\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92d slept almost six and a half hours, and he felt completely refreshed, in spite of having been awake for almost 27 straight hours. That felt\u8230\'85 off somehow. Maybe the mana in his system helped refresh him faster? Another question to ask, at any rate. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Thinking of mana, he turned his senses inward and observed his mana flows, happily finding them stable and his core completely refilled at it\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s new density. This did not mean that he was anywhere near ready to try another compression, only that his mana pool was once again full. Honestly, the mana around him now was so thin compared to the evaluations that he doubted he could even attempt a third compression in these conditions at all. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 He sat up, expected a degree of stiffness from sleep, only to find he felt like he had when he was}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf4  [back in his 20\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s, which was almost 30 years ago.]}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  Still, he gingerly got to his feet and felt\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8230\'85 nothing. No pain, no stiffness, no hunger, no thirst. On the contrary, he felt energized, clear-headed and ready to take on the world. Looking around he noticed his Guide regarding him.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I believe the proper greeting in your culture would be\u8230\'85 Good morning?\u8221\'94 she made it more of a question than a statement, with a faint trace of a smile on her face.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93And good morning to you as well,\u8221\'94 he answered. \u8220\'93Did you sleep? Or do you even need such things being a projection of the System?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I did not and do not. In spite of appearing to be a biological organism, I am not actually one. While you slept, I monitored you and the time, so that I could wake you as requested if necessary.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Monitored me?\u8221\'94 Marcus\u8217\'92s face twisted in an uncomfortable expression. \u8220\'93That\u8217\'92s\u8230\'85 nice.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93It is part of my purpose. I am here to Guide you and act to preserve your life within reason. That requires me to be aware of your status.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93My\u8230\'85 status?\u8221\'94 His uncomfortable expression transitioned into an actual frown.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Yes. You may also access your status as well, by saying or thinking the command \u8216\'91show status\u8217\'92,\u8221\'94 she explained.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Show status,\u8221\'94 he repeated, causing a screen to appear before him.}
